actionAppleScript.inline: tell application "Finder"eject (every disk whose ejectable is true and local volume is true and free space is not equal to 0)end tell

source.inline:
set state to do shell script "/usr/sbin/networksetup -getairportpower en0"
if state="Wi-Fi Power (en0): On" then
	set val to {" ", "on"}
else
	set val to {" ", "off"}
end if
return val

source.inline:

if state = "1" then
set val to {" ", "on"}
else
set val to {" ", "off"}
end if
